  "instructions": [
    "preheat the binchotan grill to medium-high heat.",
    "soak 12 bamboo skewers in water for at least 30 minutes.",
    "thread the smoked mackerel, red onion, red bell pepper, parsley and mint leaves onto the skewers.",
    "brush the skewers with olive oil and season with salt and black pepper.",
